      <title>国际货币基金组织告诉亚洲央行不要过于密切地关注美联储</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/imf-tells-asian-central-banks-not-follow-fed-too-closely-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织敦促亚洲央行关注国内通胀，避免将政策决定与美联储的预期举措过于紧密地联系在一起。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/imf-tells-asian-central-banks-not-follow-fed-too-closely-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 14:23:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>独家：消息人士称，由于担心机密，俄罗斯收紧官员旅行规定</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-tightens-officials-travel-rules-due-fears-over-secrets-sources-say-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[九名消息人士告诉路透社，俄罗斯正在加大一些官员出国旅行的难度，因为担心外国势力可能会在与西方关系60多年来最严重的危机期间试图获取国家机密。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-tightens-officials-travel-rules-due-fears-over-secrets-sources-say-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 13:57:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>东盟外长敦促缅甸停止边境暴力</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-foreign-ministers-urge-cessation-myanmar-border-violence-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[东南亚各国外交部长周四敦促缅甸边境地区立即停止暴力，表达对平民福祉的担忧以及开展对话的必要性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-foreign-ministers-urge-cessation-myanmar-border-violence-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 12:33:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾与新西兰签署协议，共同关注南海问题</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-new-zealand-eye-forces-deal-share-concern-over-south-china-sea-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯和新西兰总理克里斯托弗·卢克森周四同意深化防务合作，并对菲律宾和中国在南海发生海上冲突的问题表示严重关切。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-new-zealand-eye-forces-deal-share-concern-over-south-china-sea-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 11:51:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾和新西兰将关系提升为“全面伙伴关系”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-new-zealand-elevate-relations-comprehensive-partnership-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰总理克里斯托弗·卢克森周四表示，菲律宾和新西兰将在 2026 年将关系提升为“全面伙伴关系”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-new-zealand-elevate-relations-comprehensive-partnership-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 10:44:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>从直升机到广告，印度执政党抢购了大量选举道具</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/helicopters-ads-indias-ruling-party-snaps-up-bulk-election-props-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度大选是全球规模最大的大选，拥有近十亿合格选民，竞选活动正在加快步伐，执政党印度人民党在从直升机到在线广告等资源方面领先于对手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/helicopters-ads-indias-ruling-party-snaps-up-bulk-election-props-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 09:49:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于主流媒体保持恭顺，印度莫迪的批评者转向网上</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/critics-indias-modi-migrate-online-mainstream-media-stays-deferential-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着这个世界上人口最多的国家即将于周五开始大选，印度主流电视频道和大多数报纸上几乎没有对总理纳伦德拉·莫迪进行任何批评性评价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/critics-indias-modi-migrate-online-mainstream-media-stays-deferential-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 09:46:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>缅甸不稳定局势阻碍印度遣返难民</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/myanmar-instability-hampers-indias-bid-send-home-refugees-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度安全官员表示，缅甸叛军与执政军政府之间的战斗推迟了印度将进入东北边境曼尼普尔邦的邻国无证难民遣送回国的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/myanmar-instability-hampers-indias-bid-send-home-refugees-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 08:02:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>所罗门群岛全国大选计票工作正在进行中，美国和中国密切关注</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/counting-underway-solomon-islands-national-election-watched-by-us-china-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[所罗门群岛在一天前的全国选举后于周四开始计票，不过选举官员表示，他们正在太平洋岛屿首都霍尼亚拉寻找更大的地点来计票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/counting-underway-solomon-islands-national-election-watched-by-us-china-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 07:03:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>路透调查发现，美元坚挺削弱信心，亚洲货币空头押注增加</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/short-bets-asian-currencies-mount-firm-dollar-dents-confidence-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路透周四的一项调查显示，大多数亚洲货币的看跌头寸稳固，从今年年初开始，随着强劲的美国经济数据推高美元走高，降息押注重新定价，看跌头寸稳步加强。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/short-bets-asian-currencies-mount-firm-dollar-dents-confidence-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 06:19:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
